# sdkconfig policy:
#  a) Current default: DO NOT version sdkconfig (per-dev/local)  -> keep next line
**/sdkconfig
#  b) If you prefer reproducible builds in VCS: comment the line above and commit firmware/sdkconfig
**/sdkconfig.old
**/sdkconfig.ci
**/sdkconfig.defaults.tmp

# ESP-IDF Component Manager:
#  - dependencies.lock SHOULD be committed
#  - managed_components is re-generated -> ignore it by default
**/managed_components/
#  If you want to vendor components offline, remove the line above.

